%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftelugu%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fallu-arjuns-father-allu-arvind-announces-2-crore-support-for-injured-child-in-the-stampede-and-family-report%2Farticleshow%2F116655355.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Indian%20Test%20Cricket%20Is%20On%20The%20Cusp%20Of%20Change.%20Don't%20Fear%20It%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fm2o49jb8_cricket_625x300_25_December_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYouth%20or%20experience%3F%20Old%20formulas%20or%20out-of-the-box%20ideas%3F%20Playing%20it%20safe%20or%20high-stakes%20gambles%3F%20What%20are%20the%20best%20tactical%20plans%20Indian%20Test%20cricket%20strategists%20need%20to%20draw%20up%20in%20terms%20of%20personnel%20as%20we%20head%20into%20a%20new%20year%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnless%20you%20are%20an%20extremist%2C%20chances%20are%20you%20would%20say%20the%20best%20strategy%20is%20a%20healthy%20mix%20of%20all%20of%20the%20above.%20But%20let's%20face%20it%E2%80%94that%20is%20the%20safe%20answer.%20Treading%20the%20middle%20ground%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20deciding%20which%20way%20to%20steer%20a%20team%20in%20transition%20is%20not%20the%20easiest%20thing%20to%20do.%20When%20you%20go%20neither%20this%20way%20nor%20that%2C%20there%20can%20be%20confusion%20and%20mixed%20signals%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20can%20be%20lost%20in%20translation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20cricketer%20worth%20his%20or%20her%20salt%20also%20knows%20that%20they%20can't%20adopt%20the%20ostrich%20formula%E2%80%94you%20have%20to%20be%20ready%20to%20embrace%20change.%20See%20how%20seniors%20like%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20Mohammed%20Shami%20etc%20take%20the%20young%20guns%20under%20their%20wings%20and%20also%20don't%20fail%20to%20notice%20the%20confidence%20that%20the%20youngsters%20these%20days%20exude%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20backing%20they%20are%20getting%20from%20the%20powers%20that%20be%E2%80%94both%20on%20and%20off%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Safe%20Change%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20time%20when%20fans%20broke%20out%20in%20a%20cold%20sweat%20when%20they%20thought%20about%20what%20would%20happen%20once%20Sunil%20Gavaskar%20or%20Kapil%20Dev%20or%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20retired.%20Today%2C%20the%20team%20could%20be%20minus%20a%20Virat%2C%20a%20Rohit%20or%20a%20Shami%2C%20and%20no%20one%20would%20bat%20an%20eyelid.%20In%20the%20five-match%20home%20series%20with%20England%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20there%20was%20no%20Virat%20and%20no%20Shami%2C%20and%20India%20had%20as%20many%20as%20five%20Test%20debutantes%3A%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%2C%20Devdutt%20Padikkal%2C%20Dhruv%20Jurel%2C%20Akash%20Deep%20and%20Rajat%20Patidar.%20The%2022-year-old%20Jaiswal%20was%20the%20Player%20of%20the%20Series%2C%20thanks%20to%20his%20mammoth%20tally%20of%20712%20runs%2C%20as%20he%20became%20only%20the%20second%20Indian%20batter%20ever%20to%20score%20700-plus%20runs%20in%20a%20Test%20series%20after%20the%20legendary%20Sunil%20Gavaskar.%20India%20won%20the%20series%204-1.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20that%20is%20currently%20unfolding%20in%20Indian%20Test%20cricket%20feels%20almost%20safe.%20The%20youngsters%20are%20playing%20very%20promising%20cricket%2C%20both%20at%20home%20and%20away%20(though%20more%20consistency%20is%20needed%20in%20away%20Tests).%20Indian%20cricket%20is%20in%20an%20unprecedented%20phase%20wherein%20both%20the%20batting%20and%20bowling%20supply%20lines%20are%20incredibly%20healthy.%20You%20don't%20need%20to%20look%20beyond%20four%20players%20who%20are%20playing%20in%20Australia%20currently%E2%80%94Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%20Reddy%2C%20Washington%20Sundar%20and%20Harshit%20Rana%E2%80%94to%20understand%20this.%20Don't%20focus%20on%20individual%20scorecards%20but%20on%20the%20overall%20picture%20of%20the%20impact%20youngsters%20are%20having%20in%20Indian%20Test%20cricket.%20After%20all%2C%20the%20team%20is%20being%20built%20for%20at%20least%20the%20next%20five%20to%20ten%20years%2C%20and%20the%20First-Class%20arena%20is%20throwing%20up%20some%20incredible%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EA%20Replay%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20model%20to%20boost%20youngsters%20is%20working%20and%20needs%20to%20be%20strengthened.%20In%20Gautam%20Gambhir%2C%20the%20BCCI%20has%20the%20kind%20of%20coach%20who%20doesn't%20fear%20backlash%20or%20brickbat%20as%20long%20as%20the%20long-term%20plan%20for%20the%20future%20is%20on%20track.%20The%20big%20question%20here%20is%2C%20how%20much%20of%20the%20Board's%20backing%20does%20he%20have%3F%20It's%20not%20just%20rebuilding%2C%20India%20need%20to%20start%20winning%20the%20big%20series%20under%20him.%20The%20home%20loss%20against%20New%20Zealand%20can%20be%20forgotten%20perhaps%20only%20if%20they%20win%20this%20time%20in%20Australia.%20That%20along%20with%20qualification%20for%20the%20WTC%20could%20have%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20Gambhir's%20performance%20assessment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20shouldn't%20fear%20change%20right%20now.%20Almost%20exactly%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20we%20witnessed%20a%20huge%20transition%20in%20Indian%20cricket%20when%20MS%20Dhoni%20handed%20the%20baton%20of%20Test%20captaincy%20to%20Virat%20Kohli.%20Under%20Dhoni%2C%20the%20team%20had%20reached%20the%20number-one%20spot%20in%20the%20Test%20rankings%2C%20but%20there%20came%20a%20time%20when%20they%20had%20lost%2015%20of%2023%20overseas%20Tests.%20Dhoni%20himself%20decided%20to%20step%20down%20as%20Test%20captain%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20Test%20series%20in%20Australia.%20The%20next%20chapter%20saw%20%E2%80%9CFighting%20fire%20with%20fire%E2%80%9D%20becoming%20the%20new%20Team%20India%20mantra.%20Fresh%20blood%20was%20infused%20and%20Indian%20Test%20cricket%20evolved%20as%20the%20team%20went%20on%20to%20become%20a%20real%20force%20to%20be%20reckoned%20with%20in%20the%20longest%20format%2C%20winning%2016%20away%20Tests.%20Kohli%20overtook%20Dhoni%20as%20India's%20most%20successful%20Test%20skipper%20and%20also%20became%20the%20most%20successful%20Asian%20captain%20in%20SENA%20countries%20(seven%20Test%20wins).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECurtains%20Down%20On%20An%20Era%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20stand%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20another%20tectonic%20shift%20in%20Indian%20Test%20cricket%20today.%20The%20team%20has%20moved%20on%20from%20Test%20veterans%20like%20Cheteshwar%20Pujara%2C%20Ajinkya%20Rahane%2C%20Ishant%20Sharma%20and%20Wriddhiman%20Saha.%20Ashwin%2C%20too%2C%20has%20brought%20the%20curtain%20down%20on%20his%20career.%20The%20likes%20of%20Yashasvi%2C%20Shubman%20Gill%2C%20K.L.%20Rahul%2C%20Rishabh%20Pant%20and%20Mohammed%20Siraj%20have%20been%20effectively%20integrated%20into%20the%20Test%20system.%20Jurel%2C%20Washington%20Sundar%2C%20Rana%20and%20Nitish%20Reddy%20will%2C%20in%20all%20probability%2C%20also%20follow%20suit.%20That%20effectively%20leaves%20the%20likes%20of%20Virat%2C%20Rohit%2C%20Shami%20and%20Jadeja%20as%20the%20only%20%E2%80%98super%20seniors'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Virat%20and%20Rohit%20in%20particular%2C%20time%20is%20running%20out.%20Legacy%20and%20superstar%20status%20still%20go%20a%20long%20way%20of%20course%2C%20but%20with%20the%20kind%20of%20talent%20that%20is%20knocking%20on%20the%20door%20and%20with%20%E2%80%98evolution'%20becoming%20a%20keyword%2C%20these%20two%20stalwarts%20have%20to%20start%20performing%20consistently%20if%20they%20want%20to%20continue%20playing%20Test%20cricket.%20In%2024%20Test%20innings%20this%20year%20(till%20after%20the%20Brisbane%20Test%20vs%20Aus)%2C%20Rohit%20has%20scored%20a%20total%20of%20607%20runs%2C%20at%20an%20average%20of%2026.39%2C%20with%20two%20centuries%20and%20two%20half-centuries.%20Virat%20in%20the%20same%20period%20has%20played%2017%20Test%20innings%2C%20scoring%20376%20runs%2C%20at%20an%20average%20of%2025.06%2C%20with%20one%20century.%20His%20career%20batting%20average%20in%20Tests%20stands%20at%20an%20eight-year%20low%20(47.49).%20Unless%20they%20go%20completely%20ballistic%20in%20the%20two%20remaining%20Tests%20in%20Australia%2C%20will%20we%20see%20them%20board%20the%20flight%20to%20the%20UK%20for%20the%20tour%20of%20England%20next%20year%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20fair%20to%20say%20that%20the%20jury%20is%20out%20on%20that%20one.%20It%20wasn't%20a%20surprise%20to%20see%20both%20these%20icons%20retiring%20from%20T20Is%20after%20India%20won%20the%20last%20edition%20of%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20They%20went%20out%20on%20a%20high.%20Another%20Test%20series%20win%20in%20Australia%20this%20time%20could%20be%20the%20best%20opportunity%20for%20them%20to%20bring%20the%20curtain%20down%20on%20their%20Test%20careers%20as%20well%2C%20though%20this%20is%20the%20toughest%20format%20for%20a%20cricketer%20to%20say%20goodbye%20to.%20The%20management%20knows%20very%20well%2C%20just%20like%20every%20cricket%20fan%20in%20the%20world%2C%20that%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20is%20more%20than%20ready%20to%20take%20over%20as%20Test%20captain.%20Shami%20still%20has%20to%20prove%20his%20fitness%20and%20will%20be%20given%20a%20few%20more%20chances%20of%20course%2C%20but%20with%20the%20likes%20of%20Rana%2C%20Deep%20and%20Prasidh%20Krishna%20finding%20their%20names%20on%20the%20squad%20sheet%20more%20regularly%2C%20the%20competition%20in%20the%20fast-bowling%20space%20is%20also%20heating%20up.%20Because%20of%20his%20all-round%20abilities%2C%20including%20fielding%20smarts%2C%20Jadeja%20might%20hold%20on%20longer%20than%20the%20others.%20But%20again%2C%20with%20the%20likes%20of%20Axar%20Patel%2C%20Tanush%20Kotian%20(who%20replaced%20Ashwin%20in%20India%20squad)%20and%20Tilak%20Verma%20around%2C%20he%2C%20too%2C%20will%20be%20feeling%20the%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20clich%C3%A9%2C%20yes%2C%20but%20change%20is%20indeed%20the%20only%20constant.%20No%20one%20knows%20that%20better%20than%20an%20athlete.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20a%20former%20sports%20editor%20and%20primetime%20sports%20news%20anchor.%20He%20is%20currently%20a%20columnist%2C%20features%20writer%20and%20stage%20actor)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735126380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F2m9sv32_cricket_625x300_25_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findian-test-cricket-is-on-the-cusp-of-change-dont-fear-it-7329347%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We%20stand%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20another%20tectonic%20shift%20in%20Indian%20Test%20cricket%20today.%20The%20team%20has%20moved%20on%20from%20Test%20veterans%20like%20Cheteshwar%20Pujara%2C%20Ajinkya%20Rahane%2C%20Ishant%20Sharma%20and%20Wriddhiman%20Saha.%20Ashwin%2C%20too%2C%20has%20brought%20the%20curtain%20down%20on%20his%20career.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findian-test-cricket-is-on-the-cusp-of-change-dont-fear-it-7329347%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Budget%20wishlist%3A%20Hospitals%20want%20rise%20in%20allocation%2C%20better%20PMJAY%20rates%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735126099000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fhealth%2Fbudget-wishlist-hospitals-want-rise-in-allocation-better-pmjay-rates-124122500455_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20the%20Nathealth-Hospital%20Federation%20of%20India%2C%20the%20sector%20is%20pushing%20for%20an%20increase%20in%20healthcare%20spending%20to%202.5%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20GDP%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%