omments%2C%20made%20during%20an%20event%20to%20lay%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20the%20Ken-Betwa%20river%20linking%20project%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20came%20amid%20a%20row%20over%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah's%20remarks%20on%20BR%20Ambedkar%2C%20which%20have%20attracted%20criticism%20from%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20opposition%20parties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20event%20in%20Khajuraho%2C%20PM%20Modi%20also%20said%20only%20nations%20with%20well-managed%20water%20resources%20can%20make%20progress%20and%20that%20Ambedkar's%20vision%20played%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20strengthening%20the%20country's%20water%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBaba%20Saheb%20Ambedkar's%20vision%20and%20farsightedness%20have%20contributed%20significantly%20to%20strengthening%20India's%20water%20resources%2C%20water%20management%2C%20and%20dam%20construction.%20Ambedkar%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20the%20development%20of%20major%20river%20valley%20projects%20in%20India.%20His%20efforts%20are%20also%20behind%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20current%20Central%20Water%20Commission%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PM%20said%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20he%20said%2C%20never%20paid%20heed%20to%20the%20country's%20growing%20need%20for%20water%20conservation%20and%20did%20not%20recognise%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20architect%20of%20the%20Constitution%20as%20a%20water%20conservationist.%20Congress%20and%20governance%20do%20not%20go%20together%2C%20the%20PM%20emphasised%2C%20adding%20that%20past%20Congress%20governments%20delayed%20projects%20for%2035-40%20years%20after%20laying%20their%20foundation%20stones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20major%20challenge%20of%20the%2021st%20century%20is%20water%20security.%20In%20the%2021st%20century%2C%20only%20those%20countries%20that%20have%20adequate%20water%20resources%20with%20proper%20management%20will%20move%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM's%20attack%20follows%20similar%20scathing%20remarks%20against%20the%20Congress%20over%20the%20Ambedkar%20issue%20by%20Maharashtra%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Assam%20Chief%20Ministers%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%2C%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20and%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20hit%20back%2C%20accusing%20the%20BJP%20of%20being%20hostile%20to%20democracy%20and%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20and%20the%20Sangh%20have%20always%20opposed%20the%20makers%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20protectors%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20givers%20of%20freedom%2C%20and%20the%20protectors%20of%20democracy.%20All%20these%20facts%20clearly%20indicate%20that%20the%20Sangh%2C%20BJP%2C%20and%20their%20affiliated%20organisations%20cannot%20tolerate%20democracy%20and%20the%20Constitution%20in%20any%20form%2C%26quot%3B%20Congress%20leader%20Surendra%20Rajput%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20was%20ignited%20last%20week%2C%20when%20Mr%20Shah%20said%20in%20Parliament%20that%20taking%20Ambedkar's%20name%20had%20become%20a%20fashion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EAbhi%20ek%20fashion%20ho%20gaya%20hai%20-%20Ambedkar%2C%20Ambedkar%2C%20Ambedkar.%20Itna%20naam%20agar%20bhagwan%20ka%20lete%20to%20saat%20janmon%20tak%20swarg%20mil%20jata%3C%2Fem%3E%20(It%20has%20become%20a%20fashion%20to%20say%20Ambedkar%2C%20Ambedkar%2C%20Ambedkar'.%20If%20they%20took%20God's%20name%20so%20many%20times%2C%20they%20would%20have%20got%20a%20place%20in%20heaven)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESolar%20Project%20Inaugurated%20Too%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM%20also%20inaugurated%20the%20Omkareshwar%20Floating%20Solar%20Project%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20Khandwa%20district%20virtually%2C%20and%20laid%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20the%20Daudhan%20Irrigation%20Project%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Ken-Betwa%20river%20linking%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Water%20Resources%20Minister%20CR%20Patil%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Mohan%20Yadav%20handed%20over%20two%20'%3Cem%3Ekalash'%3C%2Fem%3E%20(urns)%20containing%20water%20from%20the%20Betwa%20and%20Ken%20rivers%2C%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20who%20poured%20it%20over%20a%20model%20of%20the%20project.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PM%20said%20the%20river%20linking%20project%20will%20open%20new%20doors%20of%20prosperity%20and%20happiness%20in%20the%20Bundelkhand%20region.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20nearly%2044%20lakh%20people%20in%20ten%20districts%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%2021%20lakh%20people%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20will%20get%20drinking%20water%20under%20the%20project%2C%20which%20is%20estimated%20to%20cost%20Rs%2044%2C605%20crore.%20They%20added%20that%20nearly%207.18%20lakh%20agricultural%20families%20in%202%2C000%20villages%20will%20benefit%20from%20the%20project%2C%20which%20will%20also%20generate%20103%20MW%20of%20hydropower%20and%2027%20MW%20of%20solar%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20also%20released%20a%20commemorative%20stamp%20and%20a%20coin%20in%20memory%20of%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%2C%20whose%20birth%20centenary%20was%20on%20Wednesday.%20The%20Vajpayee%20government%20had%20proposed%20river%20linking%20as%20a%20solution%20for%20the%20country's%20irrigation%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20also%20performed%20the%20groundbreaking%20ceremony%20for%20the%20construction%20of%201%2C153%20'Atal%20Gram%20Sewa%20Sadans'%2C%20estimated%20to%20cost%20Rs%20437%20crore%2C%20at%20the%20Khajuraho%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735123800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fjcq74n18_pm-modi_625x300_25_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famit-shah-br-ambedkar-row-congress-ignored-br-ambedkars-contributions-pm-steps-up-attack-7329123%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stepping%20up%20the%20att