0inflation%2C%20which%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F6-telling-moments-from-putins-marathon-end-of-year-event-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecould%20hit%209.5%25%20in%202025%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20rein%20this%20in%2C%20the%20country's%20central%20bank%20raised%20its%20key%20interest%20rate%20from%2019%25%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-central-bank-raises-key-interest-rate-to-21-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E21%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20October%2C%20a%20record%20high%2C%20which%20has%20eaten%20into%20companies'%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussias-defense-sector-on-overdrive-but-firms-warn-of-collapse-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprofit%20margins%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20was%20expected%20to%20raise%20the%20rate%20again%20in%20December%2C%20but%20held%20off%2C%20though%20it%20may%20need%20to%20increase%20it%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20main%20question%20is%20how%20high%20the%20inflation%20will%20be%20and%20how%20the%20slowing%20down%20will%20materialize%2C%26quot%3B%20Alexander%20Kolyandr%2C%20a%20financial%20analyst%20and%20non-resident%20senior%20scholar%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20European%20Policy%20Analysis%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPutin%20has%20acknowledged%20that%20inflation%20is%20at%20%26quot%3Ba%20relatively%20high%20level.%26quot%3B%20Speaking%20at%20an%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fputin-russia-economy-pain-point-inflation-interest-rate-vtb-forum-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvestment%20forum%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20Moscow%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20he%20urged%20his%20government%20and%20the%20central%20bank%20to%20curb%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETsMAKP%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-economy-outlook-stagflation-recession-inf