nces%20fast%2C%20and%20today's%20AI%20playbook%20may%20very%20well%20become%20outdated%20in%20the%20new%20year.%20Business%20Insider%20compiled%20views%20from%20four%20Wall%20Street%20firms%20to%20see%20what%20some%20of%20the%20most%20influential%20financial%20institutions%20think%20about%20the%20future%20of%20AI.%20Here's%20what%20Wall%20Street%20is%20predicting%20about%20the%20technology%20and%20how%20you%20can%20update%20your%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224157606f-e64a-4556-816a-15c8a0d17fe7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E4%20predictions%20for%20AI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2263c5eee2-fb76-47bc-b640-d0a4affe4073%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20spending%20isn't%20slowing%20down%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20there's%20one%20thing%20that%20AI%20proponents%20and%20naysayers%20can%20agree%20on%2C%20it's%20that%20the%20technology%20is%20expensive%20to%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuilding%20data%20centers%2C%20stocking%20up%20on%20GPUs%2C%20powering%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20that%20doesn't%20come%20cheap.%20In%202024%2C%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20poured%20mind-boggling%20amounts%20of%20capital%20into%20building%20out%20AI%20infrastructure.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%20it's%20likely%20that%20Alphabet%2C%20Amazon%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20Microsoft%20will%20have%20spent%20%24222%20billion%20on%20AI%20capital%20expenditures%2C%20which%20is%20a%2050%25%20increase%20from%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-investing-strategy-stocks-data-centers-portfolio-gains-2025-ubs-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUBS%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that's%20just%20the%20tip%20of%20the%20iceberg%2C%20according%20to%20some%20Wall%20Street%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20BlackRock's%202025%20outlook%2C%20%26quot%3Bmajor%20tech%20companies%20are%20starting%20to%20rival%20the%20U.S.%20government%20on%20research%20and%20development%20spending.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3