0AI%20as%20more%20use%20cases%20emerge%2C%20many%20on%20Wall%20Street%20believe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E2025%20will%20see%20a%20widening%20field%20of%20investment%20opportunities%2C%20particularly%20in%20so-called%20Phase%203%20companies%20that%20are%20monetizing%20AI%20and%20using%20it%20to%20boost%20their%20revenue%20streams%2C%20Goldman%20Sachs%20says.%20The%20bank%20has%20identified%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnext-ai-stocks-to-buy-magnificent-7-growth-slows-goldman-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E11%20stocks%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20are%20using%20AI%20to%20increase%20their%20revenues%2C%20per%20their%20last%20quarterly%20earnings%20calls.%20They%20include%20ACV%20Auctions%2C%20Commvault%20Systems%2C%20Cloudflare%2C%20Datadog%2C%20DigitalOcean%2C%20Dynatrace%2C%20Fortinet%2C%20Gartner%2C%20Hubspot%2C%20Mastercard%2C%20and%20ServiceNow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUBS%20also%20highlights%20a%20few%20areas%20of%20the%20market%20in%20particular%20for%20investors%20to%20keep%20an%20eye%20out%20for%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%20%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20successful%20generative%20AI%20applications%20across%20a%20range%20of%20industries%2C%20including%20in%20health%20care%2C%20cybersecurity%2C%20and%20fintech%2C%26quot%3B%20UBS%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b0f410d1-3567-4ea0-8419-b095ab6fc13e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EUS%20stocks%20will%20remain%20the%20biggest%20winners%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20stocks%20have%20outperformed%20global%20markets%20in%202024%20thanks%20in%20large%20part%20to%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20large%20sums%20being%20spent%20on%20AI%20are%20paying%20off%20for%20US%20companies.%20According%20to%20Apollo%2C%20the%20US%20has%20more%20data%20centers%20than%20all%20other%20major%20countries%20combined%2C%20giving%20it%20a%20significant%20advantage%20in%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20US%20is%20experiencing%20a%20surge%20in%20corporate%20and%20research%20spending%20on%20the%20back%20of%20the%2