F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F116652432.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EUkrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20on%20Wednesday%20denounced%20an%20%26quot%3Binhumane%26quot%3B%20attack%20from%20Russia%2C%20which%20launched%20dozens%20of%20missiles%20and%20drones%20on%20his%20war-torn%20country's%20energy%20grid%20on%20Christmas%20Day.%20More%20than%2070%20missiles%2C%20including%20ballistic%20missiles%2C%20and%20more%20than%20a%20hundred%20attack%20drones.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fzelensky-condemns-russian-inhumane-christmas-attack-on-energy-grid%2Farticleshow%2F116652432.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fzelensky-condemns-russian-inhumane-christmas-attack-on-energy-grid%2Famp_articleshow%2F116652432.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fzelensky-condemns-russian-inhumane-christmas-attack-on-energy-grid%2Famp_articleshow%2F116652432.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Blake%20Lively%20To%20Gisele%20Pelicot%2C%20The%20Illusion%20That%20Is%20Women's%20Safety%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F2e6sojc8_gisele-pelicot_625x300_23_October_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20the%20common%20thread%20joining%20the%20Bangalore%20car%20crash%20claiming%20five%20lives%2C%20Blake%20Lively's%20sexual%20harassment%20complaint%20against%20her%20It%20Ends%20With%20Us%20co-star%20Justin%20Baldoni%2C%20and%20France's%20Gis%C3%A9le%20Pelicot%20rape%20trial%3F%20The%20tenuousness%20of%20the%20thread%20of%20safety%20we%20hang%20by.%20It%20can%20snap%20in%20a%20snap.%20It%20doesn't%20matter%20how%20solid%20your%20car%2C%20career%2C%20or%20conjugality%20is%3B%20it%20may%20not%20necessarily%20keep%20you%20safe.%20Then%2C%20what%20is%20even%20the%20point%20of%20doing%20anything%3F%20If%20the%20basic%20need%20to%20be%20safe%2C%20both%20physiologically%20and%20emotionally%2C%20is%20too%20much%20of%20an%20ask%2C%20how%20can%20anyone%20stay%20motivated%20to%20achieve%20anything%20at%20either%20individual%20or%20communal%20level%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbraham%20Maslow%20surmised%20at%20least%2080%20years%20ago%20that%20safety%20is%20one%20of%20the%20five%20fundamental%20needs%20of%20human%20beings.%20According%20to%20Maslow's%20%3Cem%3EA%20Theory%20of%20Human%20Motivation%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20hierarchy%20of%20human%20needs%20is%20as%20follows%3A%20physiological%2C%20safety%2C%20love%2Fbelonging%2C%20esteem%2C%20and%20self-actualisation.%20Safety%2C%20however%2C%20needs%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20an%20overarching%20holdall%20category.%20What%20is%20anything%20worth%20if%20nothing%20is%20safeguarding%20it%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20a%20long%2C%20stable%20marriage%20worth%20if%20the%20husband%20had%20been%20inviting%20strangers%20to%20rape%20the%20sedated%20wife%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20a%20sturdy%20car%2C%20facilitated%20by%20a%20hefty%20pay%20packet%2C%20worth%20if%20the%20roads%20are%20unsafe%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20are%20an%20illustrious%20career%20and%20fame%20worth%20if%20they%20don't%20ensure%20a%20safe%20work%20environment%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWomen%20And%20Vulnerability%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Maslow's%20theory%2C%20the%20satisfaction%20of%20lower-level%20needs%20facilitates%20satisfying%20the%20next%20higher-level%20need.%20Sans%20safety%2C%20no%20need%20is%20ever%20fully%20met.%20The%20need%20for%20safety%20is%20also%20to%20be%20understood%20from%20a%20gendered%20perspective.%20Are%20women%20ever%20capable%20of%20reaching%20the%20top%20of%20the%20pyramid%20and%20meeting%20their%20self-actualisation%20goals%20if%20they%20have%20to%20be%20constantly%20watching%20over%20their%20shoulders%3F%20Or%2C%20have%20women%20trained%20themselves%20differently%20to%20see%20safety%20as%20an%20elusive%2C%20unattainable%20concept%2C%20and%20they%20are%20carrying%20on%20regardless%3F%20Have%20women%2C%20in%20other%20words%2C%20self-actualised%20as%20essentially%20vulnerable%20human%20beings%3F%20Perhaps%20so.%20Because%20this%20is%20the%20only%20way%20they%20are%20allowed%20to%20operate.%20Accepting%20their%20vulnerability%20and%20putting%20up%20their%20fences%20is%20what%20they%20have%20been%20getting%20good%20at.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20involves%20a%20process%20of%20becoming%20a%20less-than-human%20entity.%20A%20focus%20on%20women's%20bodies%20leads%20to%20%E2%80%9Cwomen%20to%20be%20perceived%2C%20and%20to%20behave%2C%20more%20like%20object%20and%20less%20like%20a%20human%2C%E2%80%9D%20psychologists%20Nathan%20A.%20Heflick%20and%20Jamie%20L.%20Goldenberg%20concluded%20in%20their%20study%20of%20literal%20objectification.%20The%20most%20damning%20indictment%20of%20the%20gender%20status%20quo%20of%20our%20world%20comes%20as%20follows%3A%20%E2%80%9CWomen%20themselves%20also%20behave%20more%20like%20objects%20(by%2C%20e.g.%2C%20speaking%20less)%20when%20they%20are%20aware%20of%20this%20focus%20by%20others%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20The%20'Code'%20Is%20Broken%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen's%20need%20for%20safety%20has%20been%20marginalised%2C%20unless%20it%20is%20fetishised%2C%20for%20so%20long%20that%20anyone%20asserting%20it%20makes%20the%20headlines.%20It%20is%20seen%20as%20something%20radical%20and%2C%20ironically%2C%20destructive.%20Women's%20need%20for%20safety%20hurts%20men's%20need%20to%20always%20be%20in%20control.%20By%20not%20continuing%20to%20be%20objects%2C%20women%20break%20the%20code.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20historical%20Gis%C3%A9le%20Pelicot%20rape%20trial%2C%20Dominique%20Pelicot%20stated%20that%20the%20trial%20had%20ruined%20his%20life%20and%20family.%20Coming%20from%20a%20man%20pronounced%20guilty%20of%20programming%20an%20elaborate%20rape-my-drugged-wife%20activity%20for%20almost%20a%20decade%2C%20the%20sentiment%20is%20dark%20and%20sinister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20in%20the%20Blake%20Lively-Justin%20Baldoni%20case%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20safe%20workplace%20environment%20was%20touted%20as%20a%20problem%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20addressed%20only%20by%20destroying%20Lively's%20reputation.%20Women%20are%20not%20supposed%20to%20ask%20for%20safeguards%2C%20even%20from%20men%20who%20claim%20to%20be%20safeguarding%20women%E2%80%94Baldoni%20received%20the%20Voices%20of%20Solidarity%20Award%20on%209%20December%20from%20the%20Vital%20Voices%20Global%20Partnership%20for%20his%20commitment%20to%20women's%20empowerment.%20What%20does%20it%20tell%20us%20about%20the%20dispensability%20of%20women's%20equal%20rights%20when%20even%20an%20%E2%80%98ally'%20finds%20it%20difficult%20to%20stop%20being%20a%20garden%20variety%20workplace%20harasser%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20it%20feels%20that%20only%20women%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20feel%20safe.%20It's%20as%20if%20almost%20everyone%2C%20including%20many%20women%2C%20has%20accepted%20it%2C%20too.%20When%20an%20accident%20happens%20on%20the%20road%2C%20a%20process%20of%20accountability%20assignation%20kickstarts.%20Who's%20at%20fault%20may%20come%20later%2C%20but%20at%20least%20there%20is%20no%20quest%20for%20the%20perfect%20victim.%20Women's%20lives%20are%20shattered%20by%20multiple%20metaphorical%20car%20crashes%2C%20and%20they%20mostly%20go%20unnoticed.%20If%20women%20demand%20safety%2C%20they%20are%20labelled%20as%20destructive%2C%20difficult%2C%20delusional%20or%20deranged%2C%20depending%20on%20what%20the%20flavour%20of%20the%20month%20is.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20does%20not%20make%20sense%20anymore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E