%20Overhauls%20Express%20Entry%20System%2C%20New%20Rules%20To%20Impact%20Indian%20Aspirants%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20professionals%20seeking%20to%20migrate%20to%20Canada%20for%20better%20job%20opportunities%20may%20face%20new%20challenges%2C%20as%20the%20North%20American%20country%20announced%20significant%20changes%20to%20its%20Express%20Entry%20immigration%20system.%20Changes%20have%20been%20introduced%20in%20the%20Comprehensive%20Ranking%20System%20(CRS)%20that%20governs%20the%20eligibility%20of%20a%20candidate%20for%20a%20permanent%20immigration%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20recent%20release%20issued%20by%20the%20Canadian%20government%2C%20the%20new%20change%2C%20under%20which%20candidates%20will%20no%20longer%20receive%20additional%20points%20for%20having%20a%20job%20offer%2C%20will%20be%20instituted%20as%20early%20as%20spring%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Did%20The%20Government%20Say%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%2C%20introduced%20as%20a%20temporary%20measure%2C%20is%20aimed%20at%20curbing%20fraudulent%20immigration%20practices%20by%20removing%20the%20incentive%20to%20illegally%20buy%20or%20sell%20labour%20market%20impact%20assessments%20to%20improve%20a%20candidate's%20chances%20of%20being%20selected%20to%20come%20to%20Canada%20as%20a%20permanent%20resident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20taking%20important%20steps%20to%20reduce%20fraud%20while%20continuing%20to%20attract%20the%20skilled%20talent%20our%20economy%20needs%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Marc%20Miller%2C%20Canada's%20Minister%20of%20Immigration%2C%20Refugees%20and%20Citizenship.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImmigration%20has%20always%20been%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20Canada's%20success%2C%20and%20we%20remain%20committed%20to%20welcoming%20the%20best%20and%20brightest%20to%20Canada%20so%20that%20everyone%20has%20access%20to%20the%20quality%20jobs%2C%20homes%20and%20supports%20they%20need%20to%20thrive%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Is%20Impacted%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20removal%20of%20CRS%20points%20for%20a%20job%20offer%20is%20instituted%2C%20the%20changes%20will%20impact%20candidates%20pursuing%20permanent%20residence%20through%20the%20Express%20Entry%20system%2C%20including%20those%20currently%20working%20in%20Canada%20temporarily.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20the%20change%20is%20introduced%2C%20it%20will%20apply%20to%20all%20candidates%20with%20job%20offers%20in%20the%20pool%20as%20well%20as%20new%20candidates%20entering%20the%20pool%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20government%20said.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Gets%20Immunity%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20new%20rules%20won't%20impact%20candidates%20who%20have%20already%20been%20invited%20to%20apply%20for%20permanent%20residence%20(PR)%20with%20a%20CRS%20score%20that%20still%20includes%20points%20for%20a%20job%20offer%20(under%20the%20%26quot%3Barranged%20employment%26quot%3B%20criteria).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20also%20not%20apply%20to%20candidates%20who%20have%20already%20submitted%20an%20application%20for%20PR%20to%20Immigration%2C%20Refugees%20and%20Citizenship%20Canada%20(IRCC)%20which%20is%20currently%20being%20processed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20the%20Express%20Entry%20Immigration%20System%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpress%20Entry%20is%20Canada's%20flagship%20online%20system%20that%20is%20used%20to%20manage%20immigration%20applications%20of%20skilled%20workers%20from%20programs%20including%20the%20Federal%20Skilled%20Worker%20Program%2C%20Federal%20Skilled%20Trades%20Program%2C%20and%20Canadian%20Experience%20Class%2C%20as%20well%20as%20parts%20of%20the%20Provincial%20Nominee%20Program.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnUnder%20the%20system%2C%20eligible%20candidates%20can%20create%20their%20profiles%20on%20the%20official%20website%20and%20enter%20the%20pool.%20Then%20candidates%20with%20the%20most%20points%20in%20rounds%20are%20invited%20by%20the%20Canadian%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20receiving%20the%20application%2C%20candidates%20are%20invited%20to%20apply%20for%20the%20permanent%20residence%20(PR)%20programme%2C%20they%20have%20to%20fill%20out%20the%20application%2C%20which%20will%20be%20reviewed%20by%20the%20government%20and%20a%20decision%20will%20be%20taken.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECanada%20Ends%20Flagpoling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Justine%20Trudeau%20government%2C%20as%20part%20of%20Canada's%20Border%20Plan%2C%20also%20announced%20that%20work%20and%20study%20permits%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20provided%20to%20flagpolers%20at%20a%20port%20of%20entry%2C%20effective%20immediately.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFlagpoling%20occurs%20when%20foreign%20nationals%20who%20hold%20temporary%20resident%20status%20in%20Canada%2C%20leave%20Canada%20and%2C%20after%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20United%20States%20or%20St.%20Pierre%20and%20Miquelon%2C%20re-enter%20to%20access%20immigration%20services%20at%20a%20port%20of%20entry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20practice%20has%20taken%20up%20significant%20resources%20at%20the%20border%2C%20diverting%20Canadian%20and%20American%20officers%20away%20from%20important%20enforcement%20activities%20and%20has%20contributed%20to%20wait%20times%20for%20cross-border%20travellers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20government%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735116180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F07dmtsl_canada-immigration-reuters_625x300_02_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcanada-overhauls-express-entry-system-new-rules-to-impact-indian-aspirants-7328362%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20professionals%20seeking%20to%20migrate%20to%20Canada%20for%20better%20job%20opportunities%20may%20face%20new%20challenges%2C%20as%20the%20North%20American%20country%20announced%20si