rative%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20national%20convener%20said%20BJP%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bhalf-government%26quot%3B%20in%20Delhi%20with%20seven%20MPs%20and%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor.%20%26quot%3BIn%20these%2010%20years%2C%20they%20did%20not%20build%20a%20single%20road%2C%20hospital%2C%20school%2C%20or%20college.%20Delhi's%20people%20gave%20them%20one%20job%3A%20law%20and%20order.%20They%20ruined%20that%20too.%20People%20are%20living%20in%20fear.%20They%20can't%20say%20what%20work%20they%20have%20done%20and%20what%20they%20will%20do%20if%20you%20vote%20for%20them.%20They%20are%20just%20abusing%20Kejriwal%20and%20asking%20for%20votes.%20They%20have%20no%20Chief%20Minister%20face%20or%20agenda%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20running%20a%20positive%20campaign.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20telling%20people%20about%20our%20work%2C%20we%20bettered%20schools%2C%20and%20hospitals%2C%20provided%20free%20power%20round%20the%20clock%2C%20gave%20water%20supply%2C%20brought%20free%20bus%20rides%20for%20women%2C%20pilgrimages%20for%20elderly.%20And%20then%20we%20are%20asking%20for%20votes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20said%20there%20is%20immense%20excitement%20among%20Delhi%20residents%20to%20register%20for%20Mahila%20Samman%20Yojana%20promising%20Rs%202%2C100%20for%20women%20every%20month%20and%20Sanjeevani%20Yojana%20for%20free%20treatment%20to%20the%20elderly.%20%26quot%3BThis%20has%20rattled%20the%20BJP%2C%20we%20have%20come%20to%20know%20from%20our%20sources%20that%20ED%2C%20CBI%20and%20Income%20Tax%20have%20met.%20There%20are%20orders%20from%20the%20top%20to%20arrest%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Atishi%20in%20a%20false%20case.%20Before%20that%2C%20senior%20AAP%20leaders%2C%20including%20me%2C%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%2C%20Satyendra%20Jain.%20The%20objective%20is%20to%20distract%20us%20from%20the%20poll%20campaign%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20leader%20alleged%20that%20a%20false%20case%20is%20being%20prepped%20against%20Atishi%20in%20the%20Delhi%20transport%20department%20and%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20stop%20free%20bus%20rides%20for%20women.%20%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20people%20will%20reply%20to%20this%20dirty%20conspiracy.%20The%20people%20of%20this%20country%20do%20not%20support%20this%20kind%20of%20politics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BNotices%20Are%20Lies%26quot%3B%3A%20Atishi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Atishi%20said%20that%20truth%20shall%20prevail%20even%20if%20she%20is%20arrested%20in%20a%20false%20case.%20%26quot%3BWe%20trust%20the%20judiciary.%20They%20sent%20all%20our%20top%20leaders%20to%20jail%20in%20false%20cases%2C%20but%20the%20truth%20eventually%20came%20out%20and%20they%20got%20bail.%26quot%3B%20She%20said%20the%20BJP%20must%20know%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bpeople%20are%20watching%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20newspaper%20notices%20issued%20by%20Delhi's%20health%20and%20women%20and%20child%20development%20departments%2C%20blocking%20the%20two%20schemes%20announced%20by%20AAP%2C%20Ms%20Atishi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20notices%20published%20in%20newspapers%20are%20wrong%2C%20lies.%20BJP%20has%20pressured%20officials%20and%20got%20this%20wrong%20information%20published%20in%20newspapers.%20These%20officials%20will%20face%20administrative%20as%20well%20as%20police%20action.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20notice%20that%20said%20there%20was%20no%20Mahila%20Samman%20Yojana%2C%20she%20held%20up%20a%20piece%20of%20paper%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDelhi%20government%20has%20taken%20a%20cabinet%20decision%20on%20the%20Mahila%20Samman%20Yojana%20and%20this%20notification%20is%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20We%20have%20notified%20the%20scheme%20to%20provide%20Rs%201%2C000%20per%20month%20to%20women.%20Later%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20gave%20a%20guarantee%20that%20we%20would%20provide%20Rs%202%2C100%20per%20month%20when%20we%20form%20the%20government%20after%20the%20election.%20He%20also%20announced%20Sanjeevani%20Yojana%20to%20provide%20free%20medical%20treatment%20to%20the%20elderly.%20This%20is%20clearly%20AAP's%20announcement%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20guarantee%20that%20Sanjeevani%20will%20be%20brought%20and%20amount%20hiked%20to%20Rs%202%2C100%20after%20the%20government%20is%20formed.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735111500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fq1pilngo_kejriwal-atishi_625x300_25_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fatishi-will-be-arrested-in-fake-case-ahead-of-delhi-polls-alleges-arvind-kejriwal-7327667%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Central%20agencies%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20arrest%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Atishi%20in%20a%20fake%20case%20and%20raid%20the%20homes%20of%20all%20senior%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20leaders%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20disrupt%20the%20party's%20Assembly%20polls%20preparations%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20said%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fatishi-will-be-arrested-in-fake-case-ahead-of-delhi-polls-alleges-arvind-kejriwal-7327667%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Markets%20down%2011%25%20in%20last%202%20months%3A%20Motilal%20explains%20where%20to%20invest%20in%202025%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735110725000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmarkets-down-11-in-last-2-months-motilal-explains-where-to-invest-in-2025-124122500231_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20latest%20correction%20in%20Indian%20markets%20has%20cooled%20off%20valuations%20in%20large-caps%2C%20Motilal%20Oswal%20Wealth%20Management%20is%20bullish%20on%20IT%2C%20healthcare%2C%20BFSI%20amo