amily%20of%20four%20Indians%20-%20from%20Dingucha%20village%20in%20Gujarat's%20Gandhinagar%20district%20-%20in%20January%202022%3B%20their%20bodies%20were%20found%20frozen%2C%20in%20-35%20degrees%20Celsius%20weather%2C%20on%20the%20Canadian%20side%20of%20the%20border.%20Inquiries%20since%20suggest%20they%20paid%20human%20smugglers%20an%20exorbitant%20sum%20-%20at%20least%20Rs%2055%20lakh%20each%20-%20to%20be%20illegally%20transported%20into%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED's%20inquiry%20-%20into%20money%20laundering%20and%20associated%20financial%20crimes%20-%20followed%20police%20in%20Gujarat's%20Ahmedabad%20filing%20a%20complaint%20against%20Bhavesh%20Ashokbhai%20Patel%2C%20the%20principal%20accused%20in%20the%20Dingucha-Canada%20deaths%20case%2C%20and%20a%20few%20others%2C%20who%20%26quot%3Bhatched%20a%20well-planned%20conspiracy%20to%20send%20people%20(Indians)%20to%20the%20United%20States%20through%20Canada%2C%20via%20illegal%20channels...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20federal%20agency%2C%20the%20modus%20operandi%20was%20to%20get%20their%20'clients'%20admitted%20to%20certain%20colleges%20in%20Canada%20-%20with%20whom%20a%20deal%20had%20been%20struck%20-%20and%20so%20get%20student%20visas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20in%20Canada%20the%20'clients'%20would%20be%20smuggled%20across%20the%20border%20and%20the%20money%20sent%20to%20the%20colleges%20-%20for%20'admission'%20-%20returned.%20Sources%20said%20the%20ED%20has%20identified%20two%20'institutions'%20-%20one%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20other%20in%20Nagpur%20-%20that%20had%20such%20commission-based%20deals%20with%20Canadian%20colleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'fee'%20was%20between%20Rs%2055%20lakh%20and%20Rs%2060%20lakh%20per%20person%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%20the%20ED%20raided%20eight%20places%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Nagpur%2C%20Gandhinagar%2C%20and%20Vadodara%2C%20and%20seized%20documents%20indicating%2025%2C000%20Indian%20'students'%20were%20being%20