aishnavi%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20habituated%20to%20so%20much%20screen%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThings%20peaked%20after%20one%20particular%20Maths%20class%20when%2C%20after%20spending%20hours%20learning%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F270005%2Fmaths-in-indian-monuments-ancient-science-symmetry-architecture-heritage%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20geometry%20concept%20%3C%2Fa%3Eonline%2C%20Vaishnavi%20still%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20make%20head%20nor%20tail%20of%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20the%20day%20she%20told%20her%20parents%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20just%20can%E2%80%99t%20do%20it.%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20learning%20anything.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoes%20homeschooling%20mean%20waking%20up%20late%20and%20doing%20what%20you%20please%3F%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20laughs%20Vaishnavi.%20She%20recalls%20her%20parents%E2%80%99%20firm%20instructions%C2%A0%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CYou%20need%20to%20utilise%20your%20time%20properly%2C%20follow%20a%20timetable%20and%20be%20disciplined.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20wake%20up%20early.%20Then%20exercise%20for%20an%20hour.%E2%80%9D%20The%20black%20belt%20in%20taekwondo%20(a%20form%20of%20martial%20arts)%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%20miss%20out%20on%20her%20exercise%20regime.%20%E2%80%9CThen%20I%20would%20study%20for%20the%20next%20four%20hours%2C%20followed%20by%20YouTube%20sessions%20to%20catch%20up%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F330277%2Fbengaluru-startup-stemonsters-founder-dr-sonali-dasgupta-making-science-fun-for-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20experiments%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20parents%20ensured%20that%20everything%20I%20learnt%20was%20in%20sync%20with%20what%20was%20being%20taught%20in%20school.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20afternoons%2C%20the%20young%20writer%20sat%20to%20work%20on%20her%20novels%2C%20followed%20by%20play%20sessions%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20and%20a%20round-up%20on%20the%20daily%20news%20at%20night.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20what%20do%20you%20do%20with%20all%20the%20extra%20time%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20use%20it%20to%20find%20out%20what%20you%E2%80%99re%20good%20at%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vaishnavi%20says.%20For%20instance%2C%20she%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20never%20an%20avid%20reader%20or%20writer.%E2%80%9D%20However%2C%20her%20curiosity%20was%20piqued%20when%20her%20mother%20assigned%20her%20a%20few%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F302842%2Fchildren-book-recommendations-by-indian-authors-ruskin-bond-chitra-banerjee-anu-kumar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreative%20writing%3C%2Fa%3E%20passages%20one%20day.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20where%20I%20developed%20an%20interest%20in%20writing.%20I%20used%20my%20time%20to%20watch%20relevant%20videos%2C%20develop%20a%20storyline%20for%20my%20books%2C%20and%20research%20the%20India%20of%20the%20past%2C%20people%E2%80%99s%20way%20of%20life%2C%20the%20food%20habits%20and%20the%20accommodation.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FFzpm4jWhF1g%3Fsi%3DsXQ-DWwHgiyzyL0M%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoes%20homeschooling%20make%20you%20introverted%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsidering%20you%20aren%E2%80%99t%20expected%20to%20dress%20up%20and%20go%20to%20school%2C%20participate%20in%20school%20events%2C%20have%20annual%20days%20or%20sports%20days%20to%20channel%20your%20energies%20in%2C%20there%20is%20an%20understandable%20tendency%20to%20retreat%20into%20a%20shell.%20But%20this%20is%20where%2C%20Vaishnavi%20says%2C%20your%20hobbies%20will%20play%20a%20role.%20%E2%80%9CWriting%20has%20helped%20me%20tremendously%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20skills%2C%20from%20designing%20the%20book%20cover%20to%20creating%20video%20trailers%20on%20my%20own.%20It%20has%20also%20forced%20me%20to%20come%20out%20of%20my%20introverted%20nature%20to%20promote%20my%20books%20on%20various%20platforms.%E2%80%9D%20She%20recalls%20participating%20in%20prestigious%20literary%20events%2C%20including%20three%20appearances%20at%20the%20National%20Hyderabad%20Book%20Fair%20and%20a%20chance%20to%20speak%20at%20the%20%E2%80%98Youngistan%20Nukkad%E2%80%99%20at%20the%20Hyderabad%20Literature%20Festival%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContending%20the%20assumption%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F262348%2Findia-homeschooling-tips-guidance-success-board-exams-marks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehomeschoolers%20%3C%2Fa%3Edon%E2%80%99t%20have%20friends%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20often%20think%20that%20homeschooling%20means%20an%20end%20to%20socialisation.%20But%20I%20tell%20them%20that%20I%20have%20gotten%20a%20lot%20more%20time%20to%20socialise%20after%20homeschooling.%20I%20have%20more%20friends%20now%20than%20I%20did%20in%20school.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20best%20part%20about%20being%20homeschooled%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20teaches%20one%20%E2%80%98life%20skills%2C%E2%80%99%20a%20thing%20many%20schools%20don%E2%80%99t%2C%20Vaishnavi%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20part%20of%20the%20curriculum%20my%20parents%20curated%2C%20I%20would%20wake%20up%20early%2C%20exercise%